Since you are working with ASP.NET Core, Entity Framework Core, and PostgreSQL, your .gitignore needs to cover standard .NET build artifacts, IDE-specific files, and sensitive local settings.

Here is a robust .gitignore content tailored for your project. You can copy and paste this into a file named .gitignore in your root directory (D:\Tiwala-Chain\).
